<div class="bibEntry"><p class="bib">11. Parks, Berkeley. <em>Color Theory: Selected Bibliography. </em>Monticello, IL: Council of Planning Librarians, 1975. Exchange Bibliography #886. 6 pp.</p><p class="annot">Approximately 80 books, many published before 1960, are included in this unannotated, selected bibliography. While it lists many classic titles in color theory, the publication lacks an introductory statement about its scope.</p></div>
